{{> layout/header}}

        <main class="container py-5" style="max-width: 720px;">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <div class="success-confetti">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size: 5rem;">task_alt</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold text-dark mb-2">예약이 완료되었습니다!</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary fw-medium fs-5">포레스트 헤이븐과 함께 즐거운 여행 되세요.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Order Number Card -->
            <div class="reservation-number-box mb-5 text-center shadow-sm bg-white">
                <span class="text-secondary small fw-bold text-uppercase tracking-wider">예약 번호</span>
                <h3 class="h2 fw-black text-primary m-0 mt-1">#RSV-20240524-001</h3>
            </div>

            <!-- Details Card -->
            <div class="fh-card shadow-sm border-0 p-4 p-md-5 mb-5 bg-white rounded-4">
                <h4 class="h5 fw-bold text-dark mb-4 d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">receipt_long</span> 예약 상세 내역
                </h4>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-1">
                    <div class="info-grid-row">
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">예약 사이트</span>
                        <span class="text-dark fw-bold">A-1 데크 (Forest View)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-grid-row">
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">이용 일정</span>
                        <span class="text-dark fw-bold">2024.05.24 - 2024.05.26 (2박)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-grid-row">
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">이용 인원</span>
                        <span class="text-dark fw-bold">성인 2명</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-grid-row">
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">결제 금액</span>
                        <span class="text-primary fw-black fs-5">150,000원</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-grid-row">
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">결제 수단</span>
                        <span class="text-dark fw-bold">신용카드 (현대 4421-****)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Action Buttons -->
            <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <button onclick="location.href='/'" class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-3.5 fw-bold shadow-lg border-0 rounded-3">예약 확인하기</button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <button onclick="location.href='/'" class="btn btn-light bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 text-secondary w-100 py-3.5 fw-bold border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3">홈으로 이동</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Info Message -->
            <p class="text-center text-secondary small mt-5 opacity-75">
                예약 내역은 마이페이지 > 예약 내역에서 언제든지 확인하실 수 있습니다.<br>
                문의 사항이 있으시면 고객센터(1588-0000)로 연락해 주세요.
            </p>
        </main>
{{> layout/footer}}
